Package domain

Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.Database
  • public final class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    In-memory object database.

    Manages objects in a centralized way.

    Needs specific opaque ids to access them and always returns clones or immutable elements.

        public Level addLevel​(Board board,
                      java.lang.String creator)

        Parameters:
        board - Board of the level.
        creator - Name of the creator of the level.

      • addGame

        public Game addGame​(java.lang.String player,
                    int level,
                    Board boardState)
        Adds a new Game with the specified player, level ID and Board state.

        Will replace it if it already exists.

        Parameters:
        player - Name of the User that played the game.
        level - ID of the level the User is playing.
        boardState - State of the current Board. Will be cloned to avoid overwriting.
        Returns:
        The newly added Game.
